The True Jesus Church is an independent Chinese church that was established in [[Beijing]], [[China]] in 1917. It belongs to the Pentecostal branch of Christianity that emerged in the 1900s. Today there are approximately 1.5 million members in forty countries. The church was established in Russia since 1995. Christmas and Easter are not celebrated.

